1 Introduction

The data we analyzed consisting of 1.351 paid and 53.567 free total websites using the technology of our main competitors and located in Turkey. The different types of websites have been spread over the types to see WEBSITES CONSTITUTED THE FIRST SEGMENT WE WILL FOCUS ON HAVE WHICH TYPE AND INDUSTRIES The dataset is exported with the help of BuiltWith Pro.

The line plots show that our competitor how many customers from Turkey our competitor web analytics services GAINED in each year between 2011-2020.
